text:
{
  "prompt": "A modern and clean computer cluster monitoring dashboard on a large screen. It displays multiple rectangular tiles showing node statuses such as CPU usage, memory usage, temperature, and task load. Each tile includes graphs, gauges, and real-time statistics. The overall layout is grid-based, dark theme with green and blue accent colors. Titles include 'Node 01', 'Node 02', etc. A summary section at the bottom shows task queue size and GPU processing status. The dashboard is designed for a 21-node cluster used in an AI computing center. The visual style is sleek, professional, and futuristic.",
  "size": "1280x720"
}

{
  "prompt": "Ubuntu Desktop 22.04 LTS GUI interface, showing a clean desktop with a left-side dock (application launcher), top bar with WiFi, volume, and power icons, open file manager window, and system settings window, modern flat design, dark theme enabled",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A modern CRM web dashboard UI for a real estate agency, featuring a clean and user-friendly design. The interface includes a customer profile card on the left with details like name, region of interest, budget, and inquiry history. In the center, there's a news and updates panel showing AI-curated property suggestions and recent newsletter entries. On the right side, a timeline of communications and automated alerts like SMS sent, call notes, and system-generated follow-ups. The color scheme is soft white with subtle accents of green and blue. Include toggles for 'newsletter subscription' and 'AI alerts' per customer.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A professional and modern CRM (Customer Relationship Management) user interface for a real estate agency. The dashboard shows an overview panel with customer engagement status, sales pipeline stages (cold call, follow-up, visit, contract, closed), AI-generated recommendations, and a calendar with appointment reminders. The interface includes tabs for 'Customer List', 'Properties', 'Messages', 'AI Assistant', and 'Analytics'. Clean layout, with a warm color theme and intuitive navigation. Real estate icons, avatars of customers, and status indicators are included.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A clean, modern CRM interface for a real estate agency. The dashboard includes sections such as 'Leads Pipeline', 'Customer Profiles', 'Upcoming Callbacks', and 'Smart AI Suggestions'. There's a sidebar with tabs like 'Home', 'Clients', 'Properties', 'Tasks', and 'Reports'. The UI is optimized for desktop and mobile, uses rounded cards, soft shadows, and minimalist icons. Branding is subtle with a white and pastel green theme. A small chatbot named '금강이' is visible in the corner, offering help.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A photorealistic virtual interior design rendering of a modern apartment based on a 34-pyeong (112 sqm) Korean apartment floor plan, featuring a living room with a white sofa and TV, a kitchen with a wooden dining table and four chairs, three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a balcony. The flooring is light-colored wood, and the design is clean and minimalist with natural lighting.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
